{"tid":1725991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中文大學同學150封親筆手稿","createTime":"2019-11-16T03:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T12:53:06.000Z","uid":212626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7b6d6a50610ceaf292bdf4ff1734afb4fd374940","tid":1725991,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:07:47.000Z","msg":"中文大學同學的親筆道歉信<br />\napologies from CUHK students<br />\n<br />\n還有更多：<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/u/0/folders/14u9cS21YaxlYGnIyiI6q4ZTIGIxUlggU?fbclid=IwAR3MCwmp8PVUklSQUHmJ7s59kapIS2ZgFpFar7jauq_Fpi5vvFLofAcpumE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Fu%2F0%2Ffolders%2F14u9cS21YaxlYGnIyiI6q4ZTIGIxUlggU%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3MCwmp8PVUklSQUHmJ7s59kapIS2ZgFpFar7jauq_Fpi5vvFLofAcpumE&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BOzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=d796c3e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/u/0/folders/14u9cS21YaxlYGnIyiI6q4ZTIGIxUlggU?fbclid=IwAR3MCwmp8PVUklSQUHmJ7s59kapIS2ZgFpFar7jauq_Fpi5vvFLofAcpumE</a><br />\n<br />\n11月12日晚，幾個議員陪同中大吳副校長到2號橋叫黨衛軍停火，還未開口，催淚彈已如雨下。我戴着初級眼罩和豬嘴，十幾秒已難以忍受，但前線是連日處身於此高危境地。昨日有法官指不會稱上街市民為「示威者」，對呀，因為他們是化學武器戰場上的戰士。<br />\n<br />\n中大同學的道歉函，看了只有慚愧。如果前面等着我們的唯有鎮壓一途，香港人會怎樣選擇呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zCck4bD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzCck4bD.jpg&h=ffc2c890&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mhGFjKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmhGFjKY.jpg&h=90042ec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSOURCE：八鄉朱凱廸 Chu Hoi Dick"},{"pid":"2c4879a584adaf251e412d792057642c03fbf5fd","tid":1725991,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:09:05.000Z","msg":"黎明行動係朝早搞，唔是夜晚搞的。<br />\n［中場檢討］係黎明行動，唔係黃昏行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1725989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1725989</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"025765c25c6477bc9aa1ce6b1df085857ef589a4","tid":1725991,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:11:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tfMxVjS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtfMxVjS.jpg&h=44a881bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YFuzpdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYFuzpdc.jpg&h=c84dc088&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2a49d8accc1eaedc3596d74e5da957d756630fd","tid":1725991,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:14:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"febe4fd4f0a995fc98e60ceb89b09b9760d7b3ab","tid":1725991,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa88b9a7a9681c9a28b681a7f1f18f6197d74514","tid":1725991,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:21:40.000Z","msg":"雙11係意圖謀殺<br />\n交通魔警係生命完全冇受威脅底下拔槍指向及射向手無寸鐵既人<br />\n仲有拎鐵騎撞向示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe243be3d3f9cfec371a49481f7c3efb186065db","tid":1725991,"uid":335348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:53:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726209/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726209/page/1</a><br />\n深度分析，大家可以都睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}